      <div data-w-id="1d07c983-3d6a-4d3d-5bc9-d7fbce51e6ec" style="opacity:0" class="about-left"><img class="about-img" src="images/sign-gemini.png" alt="A metal sign reading: BMTech; empower a sustainable future" style="opacity:0" sizes="(max-width: 2093px) 100vw, 2093px" data-w-id="1d07c983-3d6a-4d3d-5bc9-d7fbce51e6ed" loading="lazy" srcset="images/8b94941eb69acb8d526938741fe02663_sign-gemini-trans-p-500.png 500w, images/8b94941eb69acb8d526938741fe02663_sign-gemini-trans-p-800.png 800w, images/8b94941eb69acb8d526938741fe02663_sign-gemini-trans-p-1080.png 1080w, images/8b94941eb69acb8d526938741fe02663_sign-gemini-trans-p-1600.png 1600w, images/8b94941eb69acb8d526938741fe02663_sign-gemini-trans-p-2000.png 2000w, images/sign-gemini.png 2093w" /></div>
